<p> If you want to do a boat tour on the Caribbiean sea you must be attention at the animal because hit. It raises awarness about marine pollution and it's impact on human. You can also join local clean-up days and bring your friends, because every bag of trash removed makes a real difference. When you walk on the beach, pick up small plastics trahs, and don’t leave food that can attract animals and birds. It’s important to use reusable bottles and bags, so we reduce the plastic that can finish in the sea.</p>
