<p> For your vacation, you need to choose eco-friendly tours that follow the rules, keep safe distance from lacal faune, and never feed the animals. If you go snorkeling, be carefull and don’t touch the corals or the fish. At night, keep noise low and close curtains so lights don’t confuse baby creatures. Respect the signs and the seasons, because some areas are closed to protect the life cycle. </p>
